{"tid":2006744,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"55歲呂方做老豆!　３９歲女友伍惠寶佗Ｂ五個月係半億富婆","createTime":"2020-05-08T03:53:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-08T16:01:51.000Z","uid":130626,"like":80,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":73,"replies":[{"pid":"07f2781d6900969c708535c3ab7fb108495341a9","tid":2006744,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T03:53:38.000Z","msg":"今日有報導指55歲呂方做老豆，拍拖7年的39歲女友伍惠寶已懷有身孕5個月，呂方一向拍拖低調，自同鄭裕玲拍拖16年後，在2013年才被傳媒拍得同現任女友伍惠寶Rainbow拍拖，有傳今年他們已經結婚，而家再傳出女友懷孕，可以說是雙喜臨門。<br />\n<br />\n而女友伍惠寶雖然不是圈中人，但就相當有生意頭腦，她是餸菜包送公司Fresh to Go的創辧人，八年前已投資過百萬創業，據知開業第二個月已淨賺8萬，已早前她的公司更進軍電子收費平台，同不少超市及著名烹飪頻道合作，生意越做越大，有傳媒指她身家已過半億，有「網絡街市天后」稱號。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/4453484/org/8be84dedca3dc3967380a888a954092d.jpg/wIKOE3aW9H1Zc6nxWTkNlu1Vaj9Ds_RKOyMaNDsjGjQ?v=w1280r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F4453484%2Forg%2F8be84dedca3dc3967380a888a954092d.jpg%2FwIKOE3aW9H1Zc6nxWTkNlu1Vaj9Ds_RKOyMaNDsjGjQ%3Fv%3Dw1280r16_9&h=a4029d41&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3de6540981c0b362f991ada79003a60242c53e84","tid":2006744,"uid":21545,"like":7,"dislike":14,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T03:54:50.000Z","msg":"射獅子的故事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9aec21757500375c691cae9eefd0b1cc85ab8f6b","tid":2006744,"uid":56716,"like":348,"dislike":5,"score":343,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T03:55:30.000Z","msg":"原來呂方先55歲，我以為佢接近70歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d94ff6b336e63f198a90e38faaa3f566ac081de0","tid":2006744,"uid":115910,"like":139,"dislike":8,"score":131,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T03:56:14.000Z","msg":"呂方又係一個矮得黎唔會笑佢矮仔既男人黎"},{"pid":"4ef69480ebf4f4e486801e73444fa168c29ea1e2","tid":2006744,"uid":33730,"like":42,"dislike":3,"score":39,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T03:58:16.000Z","msg":"佢唱歌好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\